Class TransTransferSharedFiles

  • java.lang.Object
    • local.Transaction
      • local.TransTransferSharedFiles

  • public class TransTransferSharedFiles
extends Transaction
    Transaction remove files that can be accessed from more nodes and distribute them to other nodes. Send MsgFileRemove , receive MsgFileAck
